headline: Intercontinental Exchange (NYSE:ICE) Delivers Strong Q3 Numbers
summary: Global market infrastructure company Intercontinental Exchange (NYSE:ICE) reported Q3 CY2025 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 28% year on year to $3.01 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.71 per share was 6.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Intercontinental Exchange Approves Fourth Quarter Dividend of $0.48 per Share
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, October 30, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, announced today a $0.48 per share dividend for the fourth quarter of 2025, which is up 7% from the $0.45 per share dividend paid in the fourth quarter of 2024. The cash dividend is payable on December 31, 2025 to stockholders of record as of December 16, 2025. The ex-dividend date is December 16, 2025.
